properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St. Augustine FL out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 12 at 6:01PM EST until January 13 at 9:00AM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to less than one mile.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach
FL out 20 NM and Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St.
Augustine FL out 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM EST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM EST MONDAY
